atWithSession({channel, sessionId, message, realtimeHooks}): Promise<reply> ÔÇö legacy Web chat (deprecated by F-018)\n- createOutputHistoryService(maxEntries?): {addOutput, getHistory, clearHistory} ÔÇö F-020 per-session output ring buffer\nDEPENDENCIES:\n- uses: node:child_process: spawn for AI CLI process\n- uses: zod: config validation\n- uses: node:fs/promises: session persistence, bindings file\n- imports: src/config.js: runtime configuration\n- imports: src/security/guard.js: sanitizeInput\nKEY_FILES:\n- ai-cli-service.js: AI CLI executor with heartbeat, timeout, metrics (564 lines)\n- message-router.js: F-018 unified message processor (128 lines)\n- session-bind.js: F-018 session binding with persistence (~220 lines)\n- session-store.js: in-memory session state (427 lines)\n- realtime-hub.js: SSE event pub/sub (35 lines)\n- chat-service.js: legacy chat via codebuddy adapter (80 lines, deprecated)\n- config-service.js: F-017 runtime config manager ÔÇö hot-reload via process.env, safe key whitelist, sensitive masking (337 lines)\n- output-history-service.js: F-020 per-session output ring buffer factory (~80 lines)\nSUBDIRS:\n- src/services/output-history-service.prizm -> L2 detail for output history\nTRAPS:\n- SessionBindingService uses deferred init ÔÇö always call ensureReady() before sync methods in async contexts\n- SessionBindingService persistence is fire-and-forget ÔÇö tests must call flush() to verify file writes\n- messageRouter does not expose heartbeat hooks ÔÇö Telegram heartbeat progress disabled after F-018 migration\n- Runtime bindings created via POST /api/bind do NOT auto-subscribe realtimeHub for cross-channel push (F-018 gap)\n- config-service originalEnvValues captured at module init; if env vars set after import, use setConfig first (which lazy-captures original) before reset | FIX: ensure env vars are set before module import in tests, or setConfig will lazy-capture the pre-modification value\n- output-history-service singleton lives in output.js ÔÇö tests must inject mock via handlerCtx.outputHistoryService to avoid mutating shared singleton\nUPDATED: 2026-03-22\n","numLines":45,"startLine":1,"totalLines":45}}}
