{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01KXpqRsTsqPkuZtGPn5x1zK","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/024-web-panel-card-shadow-depth/plan.md has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ba1b8bd3-02c0-44cb-a271-5028deabbdb2","uuid":"a746eb87-c6ae-4fa8-8491-da5d828a728f","timestamp":"2026-03-22T16:48:56.689Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/024-web-panel-card-shadow-depth/plan.md","oldString":"- [ ] T1: Add box-shadow to `.panel` and `.sub-panel` in `public/styles.css`","newString":"- [x] T1: Add box-shadow to `.panel` and `.sub-panel` in `public/styles.css`","originalFile":"# F-024: Web Panel Card Shadow Depth ÔÇö Implementation Plan\n\n## Overview\n\nCSS-only enhancement to `public/styles.css`. Add `box-shadow` to `.panel` and `.sub-panel` selectors to create visual depth hierarchy against the `#f4f6fb` background.\n\n## Design Decisions\n\n- Background: `#f4f6fb` (light blue-gray), Panel: `#ffffff` (white)\n- Use rgba shadow with low opacity ÔÇö coordinates with cool-toned palette\n- `.panel` gets a more pronounced outer shadow (card lifts from background)\n- `.sub-panel` gets a lighter/subtler inner shadow (nested card, slightly less elevated)\n- No media-query-specific shadow overrides needed ÔÇö shadows are resolution-independent\n\n## Shadow Values\n\n- `.panel` box-shadow: `0 2px 8px rgba(31, 38, 51, 0.08), 0 1px 2px rgba(31, 38, 51, 0.04)`\n  - Two-layer shadow: soft ambient (8px blur, 8% opacity) + tight contact (2px blur, 4% opacity)\n  - Color: --text (#1f2633) converted to rgba for cool-tone coordination\n- `.sub-panel` box-shadow: `0 1px 4px rgba(31, 38, 51, 0.06)`\n  - Single-layer softer shadow ÔÇö visually subordinate to parent .panel\n\n## Files to Modify\n\n- `public/styles.css` ÔÇö add box-shadow to `.panel, .sub-panel` selector block\n\n## Tasks\n\n- [ ] T1: Add box-shadow to `.panel` and `.sub-panel` in `public/styles.css`\n- [ ] T2: Verify acceptance criteria (visual inspection of CSS rules)\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":26,"oldLines":5,"newStart":26,"newLines":5,"lines":[" "," ## Tasks"," ","-- [ ] T1: Add box-shadow to `.panel` and `.sub-panel` in `public/styles.css`","+- [x] T1: Add box-shadow to `.panel` and `.sub-panel` in `public/styles.css`"," - [ ] T2: Verify acceptance criteria (visual inspection of CSS rules)"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
